    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>BLOOD=BULLETS</strong> is a bullet hell boss rush action platformer where you dash into bullets to refill ammo. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In order to kill the blood itself, one must hack into the sequence.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254130/extras/0dcea15d30f10eec2455ea6855fece77.poster.avif?t=1729616875\" width=571 height=64 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254130/extras/0dcea15d30f10eec2455ea6855fece77.webm?t=1729616875\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Instead of avoiding bullets at all cost - dash yourself through as many, to refill your ammo.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254130/extras/bcbe9b2ba93d6fc18cb9d3474626ea9a.poster.avif?t=1729616875\" width=800 height=362 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254130/extras/bcbe9b2ba93d6fc18cb9d3474626ea9a.webm?t=1729616875\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254130/extras/bcbe9b2ba93d6fc18cb9d3474626ea9a.mp4?t=1729616875\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254130/extras/ae78ee3c145a29e459425bb921c2005a.poster.avif?t=1729616875\" width=571 height=63 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254130/extras/ae78ee3c145a29e459425bb921c2005a.webm?t=1729616875\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dash and shoot your way through 6 unique challenging bosses with ultra responsive and fast controls.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254130/extras/ed7ca05390eb9e7f248567f2f0582d1c.poster.avif?t=1729616875\" width=654 height=396 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254130/extras/ed7ca05390eb9e7f248567f2f0582d1c.webm?t=1729616875\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254130/extras/ed7ca05390eb9e7f248567f2f0582d1c.mp4?t=1729616875\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254130/extras/19624b6503f6395866d209cf74981e4e.apng?t=1729616875\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254130/extras/19624b6503f6395866d209cf74981e4e.poster.avif?t=1729616875\" class=\"bb_img\" width=571 height=64 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hack into the main cortex of the blood matrix, followed by stylish 1-bit  pixel art and retro soundtrack.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254130/extras/2d97ea034ca72e78b8785bcefe252d9c.poster.avif?t=1729616875\" width=800 height=320 ><source 